住生活或共同抚养照顾孙辈在我国较为普遍，在经济较宽裕的情况下对子女进行帮扶，开支部分家用亦符合情理，也有利于家庭关系的美满和谐。本案中，在二老照顾孩子期间，小杨向老周汇款补贴家用，并通过淘宝购物为孩子购买日常玩具用品，小杨并非未尽到抚养义务；老何与老周虽支付了小小何的部分费用，但小杨通过微信向老周的转款远高于有证据支持的款项；引发本案的根本原因是小杨提起了离婚诉讼，家庭矛盾激化产生。二老要求小何与小杨支付近六年的抚养费23万余元，缺乏证据支持，法院不予支持。重庆一对老人诉请儿子儿媳支付“带孙费”被驳回"},"attached_info":"Cj4I7dbGzYuAz8t4EAMaCDgzMjc3NDIxINzN4pYGMAI4XEAYcgk1NDQ0Nzc0NzR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"56 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-a0757acb8813195a76c7489e07557ae7_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"25_1658506626.6713054","card_id":"Q_28087919","target":{"id":28087919,"title":"你是什么时候发现人和人差距大得无法跨越？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/28087919","type":"question","created":1423480556,"answer_count":5473,"follower_count":72179,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[8198,107217],"comment_count":97,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"我指的差距是全方位的差距。 镜像问题：你是什么时候发现人和人的差距是可能被跨越的？"},"attached_info":"Cj4I7dbGzYuAz8t4EAMaBzM0MTc3MzUg7K3ipgUwYTjzswRAGXIIMjgwODc5MTl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"55 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/9a614cd4381538d6f58aaaf9a14fe8a3_r.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"26_1658506626.6719337","card_id":"Q_544749705","target":{"id":544749705,"title":"如果家人不同意去读高中，让我打工供弟弟读书，我应该答应还是不答应?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/544749705","type":"question","created":1658474321,"answer_count":51,"follower_count":60,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[4570,132529,153052],"comment_count":1,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4I7dbGzYuAz8t4EAMaCDgzMzM4MjUxINGe6ZYGMAE4PEAacgk1NDQ3NDk3MDV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==